## 🚀 사용 예제

### 1. 분산 양자 작업 제출
```javascript
import { QuantumCluster, DistributedScheduler } from './distributed-quantum-processor.js';

const cluster = new QuantumCluster(4);  // 4-노드 클러스터
const scheduler = new DistributedScheduler(cluster);

const jobs = [
  { jobId: 'job-001', qubits: 100, preferredType: 'GPU', estimatedTime: 200 },
  { jobId: 'job-002', qubits: 80, preferredType: 'GPU', estimatedTime: 150 }
];

const result = scheduler.scheduleJobs(jobs);
console.log(`Scheduled: ${result.scheduled}/${result.total}`);
```

### 2. 네트워크 양자 상태 라우팅
```javascript
import { QuantumNetworkTopology, QuantumStateRouter } from './network-quantum-computing.js';

const topology = new QuantumNetworkTopology();
const node1 = new QuantumNetworkNode('node-1', { lat: 37.7749, lon: -122.4194 });
const node2 = new QuantumNetworkNode('node-2', { lat: 34.0522, lon: -118.2437 });

topology.addNode(node1);
topology.addNode(node2);
topology.addLink('node-1', 'node-2', 15, 1000);

const router = new QuantumStateRouter(topology);
const tx = router.transmitQuantumState('node-1', 'node-2', 'state-001', 1000);
console.log(`Transmission reliability: ${tx.reliability}`);
```

### 3. 확장성 최적화 및 성능 예측
```javascript
import { ProblemPartitioner, PerformancePredictor } from './scalability-optimizer.js';

// 1000 큐빗 문제를 256 큐빗 단위로 분할
const partitioner = new ProblemPartitioner(1000, 256);
const partition = partitioner.partition('balanced');
console.log(`Partitions: ${partition.partitionCount}`);

// 성능 모델 학습 및 예측
const predictor = new PerformancePredictor();
predictor.collectMetric({ problemSize: 100, executionTime: 150, qubits: 50, gates: 500 });
predictor.collectMetric({ problemSize: 200, executionTime: 280, qubits: 100, gates: 1000 });
predictor.collectMetric({ problemSize: 400, executionTime: 550, qubits: 200, gates: 2000 });
predictor.trainModel();

const prediction = predictor.predictPerformance(800);
console.log(`Predicted execution time: ${prediction.predictedTime}ms`);
```

### 4. 실시간 성능 모니터링
```javascript
import { PerformanceMonitor } from './performance-monitor.js';

const monitor = new PerformanceMonitor();
monitor.startMonitoring();

// 메트릭 수집
for (let i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
  const result = monitor.collectMetrics();
  console.log(`Bottlenecks detected: ${result.bottlenecksDetected}`);
}

const status = monitor.getMonitoringStatus();
console.log(`Alerts triggered: ${status.alertInfo.totalAlerts}`);
```

